org.sql: SELECT issues.* FROM issues INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = issues.project_id WHERE issues.created_on BETWEEN '2022-02-04' AND '2022-02-14' AND issues.author_id = 2 AND projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'issue_tracking') IS NOT NULL
